<L>__{exterior moslem quarter day}
<A>__{from the pov of the two arabs following him, we see carlos lost, or pretending to be, as he ambles along through the suq, past all sorts of vendors hawking their wares. heads of fish are cut off with the swift slash of a knife in one stall, freshly skinned lambs hang by their feet in another. carlos, still looking lost, approaches a street vendor hawking rosary beads. we see them talk but cannot hear their dialogue. carlos walks on.}
